OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1774465894
OL,3,CDrink-driver disqualified for head-on
OL,4,Ccrash which gives victim 'flashbacks'
OL,6,FA drink-driver from Chichester has
OL,7,Fbeen banned from the roads for two
OL,8,Fyears after causing a head-on
OL,9,Fcollision which still gives the 20-
OL,10,Fyear-old victim "flashbacks".
OL,12,FJames Lamont, 28, was travelling west
OL,13,Fin his Audi Q2 on the A259 Bognor Road
OL,14,Ftowards Chichester on 10 August 2025
OL,15,Fwhen he crossed into the opposing
OL,16,Fcarriageway.
OL,18,FLamont, of Anna Sewell Road, crashed
OL,19,Finto an oncoming BMW 3 Series which
OL,20,Fwas being driven on the correct side
OL,21,Fof the road at around 4am.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
