OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1774465894
OL,3,CDrink-driver disqualified for head-on
OL,4,Ccrash which gives victim 'flashbacks'
OL,6,FThe passenger in the BMW car ` a 20-
OL,7,Fyear-old man from Bognor ` sustained a
OL,8,Fbroken leg which continues to affect
OL,9,Fhim in everyday life.
OL,11,FIn his victim impact statement written
OL,12,Fafter the collision, he said: "I still
OL,13,Fget what I consider to be PTSD when I
OL,14,Fam the passenger in cars.
OL,16,F"I receive flashbacks three or four
OL,17,Ftimes a week, sometimes at work, and
OL,18,Fthese flashbacks include a pair of
OL,19,Fheadlights coming straight towards me.
OL,26,@tD@_OU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1774465894
OL,3,CDrink-driver disqualified for head-on
OL,4,Ccrash which gives victim 'flashbacks'
OL,6,F"This brings my recollection of the
OL,7,Finitial impact immediately back to my
OL,8,Fmind."Prior to the collision, I was
OL,9,Fgetting into kickboxing and had been a
OL,10,Fcouple of times.
OL,12,F"I had been pursuing this new hobby
OL,13,Fbut now I don't know if the metal rod
OL,14,Fin my leg and my level of flexibility
OL,15,Fwill allow me to continue."
OL,17,F"This incident has significantly
OL,18,Faffected my work, my relationship, my
OL,19,Fmental health, home life and
OL,20,Feverything in between.
OL,26,@pD@FOUwD@[OU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
