PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1774465894
OL,3,CDrink-driver disqualified for head-on
OL,4,Ccrash which gives victim 'flashbacks'
OL,6,F"I just want to get back to my full
OL,7,Froutine, back to work property, back
OL,8,Fto the gym, back to doing the things I
OL,9,Flove with my friends and family. Back
OL,10,Fto normality."
OL,12,FLamont pleaded guilty to all offences
OL,13,Fat Worthing Magistrates' Court on 3
OL,14,FMarch 2026,
OL,16,FAlongside his driving ban, he was
OL,17,Fsentenced to a 12-month community
OL,18,Forder, requiring him to carry out 200
OL,19,Fhours of unpaid work.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@NO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
